item.title: INF 554 Assignment 1
item.description: Notes for INF 554 Assignment 1 Useful Data Source It is easy to publish chart on Google Sheet with following steps: 1 In the top right of chart, click More. 2 Click Publish chart. 3 Choose a publishing option: * Link: Copy and share the link. * Embed: Copy and paste the HTML code into your website or blog. 4 Select the sheet with the chart and click Publish.
